**Variability in Definitions:**
Labels that have same or similar names do not necessarily cover similar texts. [cite_start]For instance, the label "Article" in Genre-KI-04 includes research articles, reviews, and technical reports[cite: 1020, 1021].


[cite_start]Similarly, "Journalistic" in the 20-Genre Collection includes news, reportages, editorials, interviews, and reviews[cite: 1024].


[cite_start]In the CORE dataset, "News Report/Blog" varies from objective reports to opinionated blog-like posts[cite: 1098, 1099].


